growth of population and urbanizations, which has led to greater
vulnerability. A spatio-temporal analysis of these weather extremes over
India will be very helpful to understand the vulnerability potential and
to improve the forecast skill and use these forecasts in minimizing the
adverse impacts of such weather extremes.
