simulation method to generate an ensemble nowcasting of rainfall fields.
The Var region (south eastern France) and 14 events are used to validate
the approach. Results show that the proposed method can be a solution to
combine information from radar fields and rain gauges to generate
nowcasting rainfall fields adapted for flash flood alert.
