T1  - Beyond `flood hotspots': Modelling emergency service accessibility during flooding in York, UK
A1  - Coles, Daniel
A1  - Yu, Dapeng
A1  - Wilby, Robert L
A1  - Green, Daniel
A1  - Herring, Zara
Y1  - 2017///
