material goods and landscape. Flash floods are characterized by a high
degree of risk, primarily due to reduced possibilities to make effective
forecasts, but also because of weather and climatic characteristics that
changed in the last decades, thus limiting the possibilities of
application of appropriate defense and adaptation measures.
