capacity did not necessarily lead to lower vulnerability, as the
inherent relationship among them might aggravate the vulnerability of
catchments to flash flood. Some suggestions were put forward for the
prevention of flash flood based on the vulnerability assessment.
Finally, the advantages and disadvantages of the approach were
discussed.
