AB  - In April 2013, a 7.0 Mw earthquake struck in Lushan County, Sichuan
Province, China, causing serious housing damage. Housing reconstruction
is a crucial part of disaster recovery, and resident participation has
been recognized as a key part of reconstruction success. This paper
examined housing reconstruction resident participation in the
