AB  - Post-event survey and investigation is one way to gain experience on
natural hazards. The importance of the systematisation and
standardisation of such investigations and re-analysis is progressively
recognised in all the geophysical sciences as shown by the growing
number of scientific papers and programs on the subject. But how to
proceed in the case of a flash floods, what type of data should be
