life and the huge costs that burden on society, has to consider it as a
priority. In this scenery, the activity of planning, considered as the
activity of organization of a urban settlement afterwards a rigorous and
accurate analysis of all relevant aspects, both human and natural, plays
a major role to obtain acceptable risk level.
