for the community-based restoration projects such as prevention or
preparedness, sustainable development and resilient recovering have been
suggested based on the three predicted priority ranking groups. It is
expected that the flood risk assessment ranking ensured by full
verification can help to establish optimal regional restoration plans
against flooding disasters with respect to causes and characteristics of
