often caused by torrential rains. In Algeria, floods have left more than
1000 dead and caused loss of around 550 million euros. In Mekerra Basin,
northwestern Algeria, the flooding risk is growing. This paper diagnoses
the causes and the flood damage that generates Wadi Mekerra. Besides,
